difference test

ex3.stan

data{
  int N;
  vector[N] a;
  vector[N] b;
}
parameters{
  real ma;
  real<lower=0> sa;
  real mb;
  real<lower=0> sb;
}
model{
  a~normal(ma,sa);
  b~normal(mb,sb);
}
generated quantities{
  real d;
  d=mb-ma;
}
n=20
a=rnorm(n,10,1)
b=rnorm(n,11,2)
data=list(N=n,a=a,b=b)

mdl=cmdstan_model('./ex3.stan')

data{
  int N;
  vector[N] x;
  vector[N] y;
}

parameters{
  real b0;
  real b1;
  real<lower=0> s;
}

model{
  y~normal(b0+b1*x,s);
}
# make prediction with R
n=20
x=runif(n,0,100)
y=rnorm(n,x*3+10,10)
par(mfrow=c(1,1))
plot(x,y)

data=list(N=n,x=x,y=y)

mdl=cmdstan_model('./ex4-1.stan')

  cov_matrix[2] cv;
  cv[1,1]=s[1]^2;
  cv[2,2]=s[2]^2;
  cv[1,2]=r*s[1]*s[2];
  cv[2,1]=r*s[1]*s[2];
}

model{
  y~multi_normal(m,cv);
}
